16=5\cdot3+1
\implies 1=16-5\cdot3=16-(19-1\cdot16)5=(35-19)-5(19-(35-19))=6\cdot35-11\cdot19
\implies19\cdot11=35\cdot6-1\implies 19\cdot(-11)\equiv 1\pmod {35}\implies 19\cdot24\equiv 1\pmod {35}
